  <MeleeWeapon_Hunterphage_RipperSawBlade.label>Ripper-Sägeblatt</MeleeWeapon_Hunterphage_RipperSawBlade.label>
  <!-- EN: A two-handed saw blade with a giant circular saw. The pizza cutter "circular saw" is so heavy that it takes some effort to swing it, but with the saw revving-up and the power of centrifugal force, the ripper saw blade can deal heavy amounts of damage in a single swing. -->
